### Animal Daily API Test
### 说明：这是标准 .http 请求格式（无脚本块）
### 使用方式：先执行登录/注册，手动把 token 和 id 填到顶部变量
### 注意：
### 1) @accessToken / @refreshToken 不要加引号
### 2) /auth/refresh 成功后会返回新的 refreshToken，旧 refreshToken 立即失效（需同步更新变量）

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@email = 123456@qq.com
@password = a12345678
@nickname = ApiTester
@accessToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJlM2Y5MTdjNC1iM2YwLTRkYTEtYjhkZC0xN2QxZmM3YmQwZDIiLCJlbWFpbCI6IjEyMzQ1NkBxcS5jb20iLCJpYXQiOjE3NzQ0MDk3MjksImV4cCI6MTc3NDQxMDYyOX0.RR2GNnR9O8_LZtl1XEcyrLzMVRtICZuz-b5BT7adfsQ
@refreshToken = 30107ae2313a320849f94f076c068a0d08aa007c5892f565bc59a8d81dc9d947
@categoryId =
@activityId =
@testDate = 2026-03-24
@testYear = 2026
@testMonth = 3
@attachmentId =

### 1) 健康检查
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ping
Accept: application/json

### 2) 注册
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "nickname": "{{nickname}}"
}

### 3) 登录（从响应里复制 accessToken / refreshToken 到顶部变量）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "deviceInfo": "http-client"
}

### 4) 刷新 token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 5) 登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 6) 获取用户资料
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 7) 更新用户资料
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "ApiTesterUpdated",
  "timezone": "Asia/Shanghai",
  "dailyReminderTime": "21:30",
  "reminderEnabled": true
}

### 8) 修改密码
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "{{password}}",
  "newPassword": "NewPassw0rd123"
}

### 9) 分类列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 10) 新建分类（从响应复制 id 到 @categoryId）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "TestCategory",
  "icon": "T",
  "color": "#22C55E"
}

### 11) 修改分类
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "TestCategoryRenamed",
  "icon": "R",
  "color": "#2563EB"
}

### 12) 分类排序（ids 按你实际分类 id 填）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/categories/sort
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": ["{{categoryId}}"]
}

### 13) 删除分类
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 14) 新建活动（从响应复制 id 到 @activityId）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/activities
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "API test activity",
  "level": 4,
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "durationMinutes": 60,
  "date": "{{testDate}}"
}

### 15) 活动列表（按日期）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/activities?date={{testDate}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 16) 修改活动
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/activities/{{activityId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "API test activity updated",
  "level": 5,
  "durationMinutes": 90
}

### 17) 删除活动
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/activities/{{activityId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 18) 每日总结（按日）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/daily-summary?date={{testDate}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 19) 更新每日总结（手动等级/备注）
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/daily-summary
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "{{testDate}}",
  "manualLevel": 4,
  "note": "updated by api.http"
}

### 20) 每日总结（按月）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/daily-summary/month?year={{testYear}}&month={{testMonth}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 21) 每日总结（日历）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/daily-summary/calendar?year={{testYear}}&month={{testMonth}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 22) 市场监控（公开接口）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/market-monitor?days=90
Accept: application/json

### 23) 市场监控（非法 days，测试默认值）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/market-monitor?days=abc
Accept: application/json

### 24) 未鉴权测试（预期 401）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/user/profile
Accept: application/json

### 25) AI 流式接口（需服务端配置 OPENAI_API_KEY）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/chat-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "请基于我今天的记录给我 3 条简短建议"
}

### 26) 上传 AI 附件（图片/TXT/Markdown/JSON/CSV/XML/PDF）
### 执行后，把响应 data.id 填到 @attachmentId
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

这是一个测试附件，请帮我总结 3 个重点。
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 27) AI + 附件联动
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/chat-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "请结合附件内容给我执行建议",
  "attachmentIds": ["{{attachmentId}}"]
}

### 28) AI Function Calling 验证（提示模型先调工具）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/ai/chat-stream
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "请先调用 get_daily_summary_by_date 和 get_activities_by_date 查询 2026-03-24 的真实记录，再给我 3 条具体改进建议。"
}
